    <p>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-1a' );" name="014-1a" class="pb">[014-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:190'>欽定四庫全書</span>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='190:200'>　周易總義卷十四</span>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='200:220'>　　　　　　　　　　　　宋　易祓　撰</span>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='220:225'>　下經</span>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='225:228'>革</span>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='228:242'>　　　　兑　上　　離　下</span>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='242:300'>　　　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0306' title='KR0306' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0306.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0320' title='KR0320' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0320.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0320' title='KR0320' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0320.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0320' title='KR0320' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0320.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0306' title='KR0306' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0306.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0320' title='KR0320' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0320.png'/></span>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='300:340'>　　　<span class='krp-note'>豹/變</span>　<span class='krp-note'>虎/變</span>　<span class='krp-note'>改/命</span>　<span class='krp-note'>三/就</span>　<span class='krp-note'>已日鞏用/乃革黄牛</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='340:366'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-1b' );" name="014-1b" class="pb">[014-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='366:389'>　　革之成卦離在下兊在上澤火相變為革之象革</span>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='389:412'>　　者變也黄帝堯舜氏以来變通不窮皆革之義而</span>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='412:435'>　　彖言湯武革命乃革道之大者初爻不可以有為</span>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='435:458'>　　故言鞏用黄牛伊尹耕莘大公釣渭之時也二爻</span>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='458:481'>　　中正得君可以有為故言已日乃革之伊尹就商</span>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='481:504'>　　太公歸周之時也三爻言三就則升陑孟津之役</span>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='504:527'>　　四爻言改命則南巢牧野之舉五爻言虎變則革</span>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='527:550'>　　夏反商之事爻辭皆言有孚者革而當者也上爻</span>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='550:576'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-2a' );" name="014-2a" class="pb">[014-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='576:599'>　　言貞凶居貞吉則都亳都鎬之後濟其革之過者</span>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='599:622'>　　也其他如不相襲禮不相沿樂以至改正朔易服</span>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='622:644'>　　色之類无非通變之道革之貴乎時義者如此</span>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='644:657'>革已日乃孚元亨利貞悔亡</span>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='657:680'>彖曰革水火相息二女同居其志不相得曰革已日乃</span>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='680:703'>孚革而信之文明以説大亨以正革而當其悔乃亡天</span>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='703:726'>地革而四時成湯武革命順乎天而應乎人革之時大</span>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='726:730'>矣哉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='730:756'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-2b' );" name="014-2b" class="pb">[014-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='756:779'>　　革卦之上體兊為澤非水也而彖言水火者火不</span>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='779:802'>　　宜居澤水之下取水火相息之義而已亦兊離二</span>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='802:825'>　　女同居而志不相得之意盖離火至正秋之兊則</span>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='825:848'>　　為澤水所變故曰革然聖人之有所革于天下不</span>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='848:871'>　　能使人之遽信俟其已日乃孚非革而信者乎以</span>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='871:894'>　　卦彖言之文明以説所以釋革卦上下二體之義</span>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='894:917'>　　也大亨以正所以釋革卦元亨利貞之義也是以</span>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='917:940'>　　宜革而當其悔乃可亡也彖復以天地之成四時</span>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='940:966'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-3a' );" name="014-3a" class="pb">[014-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='966:989'>　　湯武之順天應人以推明革之時義知時義之大</span>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='989:1004'>　　則知革卦之所以為大者也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1004:1020'>象曰澤中有火革君子以治厯明時</span>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1020:1043'>　　澤中有火者天地革之義也治厯何取乎革日行</span>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1043:1066'>　　之度每歳有差堯命羲和厯象日月星辰昴中之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1066:1089'>　　時日躔于虛至周已躔于牽牛其後躔于南斗嵗</span>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1089:1112'>　　差有法革之而後當所以推明天地革而四時成</span>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1112:1121'>　　之大義者也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1121:1147'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-3b' );" name="014-3b" class="pb">[014-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1147:1157'>初九鞏用黄牛之革</span>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1157:1172'>　象曰鞏用黄牛不可以有為也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1172:1195'>　　革卦之初九爻陽剛未中乃不可以有為之時故</span>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1195:1218'>　　戒之以鞏用黄牛之革此皮革也借用其義鞏者</span>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1218:1241'>　　固也黄者中色也牛者順物也中順者六二爻之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1241:1264'>　　徳何以言于初九爻初九用六二之徳而不敢以</span>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1264:1287'>　　自用故曰鞏鞏則自外而来于内與遁卦之六二</span>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1287:1310'>　　爻同辭遁言于下卦之中而革言于下卦之初初</span>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1310:1336'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-4a' );" name="014-4a" class="pb">[014-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1336:1349'>　　則尤不可以有為者也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1349:1362'>六二已日乃革之征吉无咎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1362:1375'>　象曰已日革之行有嘉也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1375:1398'>　　六二爻柔順中正臣道之善者也上應九五爻剛</span>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1398:1421'>　　柔相濟于是乎可以言革矣然臣道不可先乎君</span>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1421:1444'>　　先乎君則咎所由生故已日乃革之言革之已日</span>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1444:1467'>　　者九五爻以正應在上待其巳事之日而徃應焉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1467:1490'>　　是以行則有嘉盖君與臣相得徃吉自可无咎尤</span>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1490:1516'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-4b' );" name="014-4b" class="pb">[014-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1516:1529'>　　革卦之道至為善者也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1529:1543'>九三征凶貞厲革言三就有孚</span>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1543:1556'>　象曰革言三就又何之矣</span>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1556:1579'>　　九三爻以隂居陽位過中妄動其征必凶其道為</span>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1579:1602'>　　至危守以貞固亦為貞厲然離之體在下初爻不</span>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1602:1625'>　　可以有為二爻于已日乃革之三爻則革之而就</span>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1625:1648'>　　稽之于衆亦云可革故曰革言三就三陽数之老</span>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1648:1671'>　　者也上六爻為正應有孚也有孚則革之而當又</span>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1671:1697'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-5a' );" name="014-5a" class="pb">[014-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1697:1720'>　　何之焉言其不可舎是而他有所之已上三爻皆</span>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1720:1733'>　　以互乾卦之體為有孚</span>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1733:1744'>九四悔亡有孚改命吉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1744:1756'>　象曰改命之吉信志也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1756:1779'>　　革卦六爻之中惟九四爻不當位宜有悔也而居</span>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1779:1802'>　　澤火革之際其動也革而當悔亡矣是以下與初</span>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1802:1825'>　　六爻相應上與九五爻相比上下交信為有孚其</span>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1825:1848'>　　志既孚于人而後可以言改命改命即革命之義</span>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1848:1874'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-5b' );" name="014-5b" class="pb">[014-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1874:1897'>　　也易之取義不一故不言革而言改九四爻互巽</span>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1897:1920'>　　卦之體為命當革卦上下之變則為改命之象也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1920:1942'>　　改命于有孚之後上與下信其志所以為吉也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1942:1954'>九五大人虎變未占有孚</span>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1954:1967'>　象曰大人虎變其文炳也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1967:1990'>　　革卦九五爻言大人亦猶乾卦九五爻之言大人</span>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1990:2013'>　　也乾卦于五爻有飛龍之象革卦于五爻有虎變</span>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2013:2036'>　　之象均是大人也而象則異亦各因其時而已盖</span>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2036:2062'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-6a' );" name="014-6a" class="pb">[014-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2062:2085'>　　革之上卦兊體兊西方為虎變下與六二爻為應</span>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2085:2108'>　　六二居離體之中柔順而文明其文炳然惟革之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2108:2131'>　　大人足以當之當革之時固不待占而已為有孚</span>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2131:2145'>　　與二爻四爻之有孚異矣</span>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2145:2162'>上六君子豹變小人革面征凶居貞吉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2162:2184'>　象曰君子豹變其文蔚也小人革面順以從君也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2184:2207'>　　上六爻革道之成者也革至于五爻大人虎變其</span>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2207:2230'>　　文巳炳然至于上爻則人心從化在君子則下大</span>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2230:2256'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-6b' );" name="014-6b" class="pb">[014-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2256:2279'>　　人一等謂之豹變其文茂宻故曰蔚小人則回心</span>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2279:2302'>　　向道以正王面故曰面面取乎所向而已君子本</span>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2302:2325'>　　與君同向為成文之美小人本與君不同向亦為</span>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2325:2348'>　　順從之義當是時也何革為哉若復紛更是謂征</span>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2348:2371'>　　凶矣惟能與天下相安而歸乎常所以居貞而吉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2371:2384'>　　此持盈守成之爻也哉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2384:2387'>鼎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2387:2400'>　　　　離　上　巽　下</span>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2400:2426'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-7a' );" name="014-7a" class="pb">[014-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2426:2484'>　　　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0320' title='KR0320' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0320.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0306' title='KR0306' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0306.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0320' title='KR0320' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0320.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0320' title='KR0320' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0320.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0320' title='KR0320' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0320.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0306' title='KR0306' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0306.png'/></span>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2484:2524'>　　　<span class='krp-note'>玉/鉉</span>　<span class='krp-note'>黄/耳</span>　<span class='krp-note'>折/足</span>　<span class='krp-note'>耳/革</span>　<span class='krp-note'>有/實</span>　<span class='krp-note'>顛/趾</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2524:2547'>　　鼎之成卦巽居下離居上取象于鼎者也易之諸</span>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2547:2570'>　　卦皆言象近取諸物以為象者鼎與井而已井卦</span>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2570:2593'>　　以木巽水鼎卦以木巽火二卦皆以飬人為義故</span>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2593:2616'>　　皆實象明之今鼎卦之六爻初爻言鼎顛趾則以</span>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2616:2639'>　　隂柔在下為足二爻在下卦之中位為鼎有實三</span>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2639:2662'>　　爻在下卦之上為鼎耳革四爻應乎下卦之初爻</span>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2662:2688'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-7b' );" name="014-7b" class="pb">[014-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2688:2711'>　　為鼎折足三者皆以陽剛在中為腹五爻言鼎黄</span>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2711:2734'>　　耳則以柔居中為耳上爻言鼎玉鉉則以剛柔相</span>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2734:2757'>　　節為鉉全體皆具而後足成鼎之用也盖鼎卦之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2757:2780'>　　與井卦其用在五爻而成功皆在上爻井之卦至</span>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2780:2803'>　　上六爻而後為元吉鼎之卦至上九爻而後為大</span>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2803:2821'>　　吉皆所以全飬人之道以溥利者也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2821:2827'>鼎元吉亨</span>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2827:2850'>彖曰鼎象也以木巽火亨飪也聖人亨以享上帝而大</span>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2850:2876'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-8a' );" name="014-8a" class="pb">[014-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2876:2899'>亨以飬聖賢巽而耳目聰明柔進而上行得中而應乎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2899:2906'>剛是以元亨</span>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2906:2929'>　　鼎卦繼于革卦之後故初爻利出否否道既革鼎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2929:2952'>　　而新之斯謂之元必元吉而後可以言亨物之不</span>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2952:2975'>　　亨不知元吉之道者也彖為之推廣其象巽木居</span>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2975:2998'>　　離火之下以木巽火也巽下也以木下于火亨飪</span>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2998:3021'>　　之象也惟聖人為能極其用亨以享上帝則天道</span>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3021:3044'>　　貴乎質故其禮為亨大亨以飬聖賢則人事貴乎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3044:3070'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-8b' );" name="014-8b" class="pb">[014-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3070:3093'>　　文故備其禮而為大亨又上卦離為目五爻為耳</span>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3093:3116'>　　下巽巽也自下而上故言巽而耳目聰明盖卦自</span>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3116:3139'>　　巽来柔進而上行于五爻五爻以柔得中而進乎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3139:3162'>　　九二爻之剛中君臣以中道相孚而成革故鼎新</span>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3162:3182'>　　之功至是而後言元亨則吉亦在其中矣</span>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3182:3198'>象曰木上有火鼎君子以正位凝命</span>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3198:3221'>　　木上有火離與巽成體乃鼎之象也禹之貢金九</span>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3221:3244'>　　牧鑄鼎象物三代傳之以為有國者之大寶鎮離</span>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3244:3270'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-9a' );" name="014-9a" class="pb">[014-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3270:3293'>　　體在上位也必有大寶而後可以正離明之位巽</span>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3293:3316'>　　體在下命也必有大寳而後可以凝巽申之命至</span>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3316:3339'>　　于武王乃遷鼎于雒邑周公遂定鼎于郟鄏皆正</span>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3339:3350'>　　位凝命之大㫖也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3350:3367'>初六鼎顛趾利出否得妾以其子无咎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3367:3385'>　象曰鼎顛趾未悖也利出否以從貴也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3385:3408'>　　初六爻居卦之下為鼎趾仰而從四爻之正應則</span>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3408:3431'>　　趾反居上顛趾之象趾顛則鼎覆咎也于義為悖</span>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3431:3457'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-9b' );" name="014-9b" class="pb">[014-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3457:3480'>　　今象言未悖者何也盖鼎當致用之始欲取其㓗</span>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3480:3503'>　　新者必去其穢故者否者故穢之物也利出否以</span>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3503:3526'>　　從貴則雖顛趾而末悖易以陽為貴隂為賤初爻</span>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3526:3549'>　　之應四爻以賤從貴者也巽在互兊之下為妾三</span>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3549:3572'>　　陽爻在前為子長子主噐正鼎之象亦子貴賤妾</span>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3572:3595'>　　之義又初爻之隂柔妾也顛趾而未悖者也上從</span>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3595:3616'>　　四爻之正應子也出否從貴者也是以无咎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3616:3632'>九二鼎有實我仇有疾不我能即吉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3632:3659'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-10a' );" name="014-10a" class="pb">[014-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3659:3679'>　象曰鼎有實慎所之也我仇有疾終无尤也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3679:3702'>　　九二爻鼎之腹也正應在六五爻易以陽為實隂</span>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3702:3725'>　　為虛六五爻隂柔而虛其中九二以陽剛應之則</span>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3725:3748'>　　虛者實矣故曰鼎有實然二爻五爻雖正應而二</span>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3748:3771'>　　去五尚逺其間必有梗其進者春秋傳曰嘉耦曰</span>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3771:3794'>　　妃怨耦曰仇以六五爻言之二爻其嘉耦而三四</span>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3794:3817'>　　爻其怨耦歟三四爻以陽剛不中之才見阻于上</span>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3817:3840'>　　下交際之間二爻將柰之何哉惟謹其所之不容</span>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3840:3867'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-10b' );" name="014-10b" class="pb">[014-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3867:3890'>　　恱以詭随亦不輕躁而冒進二爻亦乗剛在上互</span>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3890:3913'>　　兊體為毁折是謂我仇有疾不我能即矣其終至</span>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3913:3936'>　　於九二爻六五爻自然相應亦無所取于我也乃</span>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3936:3950'>　　君臣相得斯謂之吉者歟</span>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3950:3970'>九三鼎耳革其行塞雉膏不食方雨虧悔終吉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3970:3982'>　象曰鼎耳革失其義也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3982:4005'>　　九三爻亦鼎之腹宜有實者也而曰鼎耳革者耳</span>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='4005:4028'>　　謂六五爻正所謂運鉉而逹其腹之所容者惟上</span>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4028:4055'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-11a' );" name="014-11a" class="pb">[014-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4055:4078'>　　无正應失隂陽相濟之義則鉉塞不行而五之耳</span>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4078:4101'>　　無所用力子其間實在其中美如雉膏誰得而享</span>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4101:4124'>　　之耶上卦離明為雉膏互兊口在下為不食不食</span>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4124:4147'>　　則烏能无悔然君子䖏已之道要使美實備于我</span>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4147:4170'>　　而不計其行之通與塞及其終三爻與二爻以同</span>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4170:4193'>　　體順乎五爻隂陽相濟有至和將雨之道此所以</span>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4193:4209'>　　虧其始之悔而終以𫉬吉也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4209:4223'>九四鼎折足覆公餗其形渥凶</span>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4223:4250'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-11b' );" name="014-11b" class="pb">[014-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4250:4262'>　象曰覆公餗信如何也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4262:4285'>　　九家京荀虞以形為刑以渥為剭重刑也音屋薛</span>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4285:4294'>　　云古文作渥</span>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4294:4317'>　　九四爻亦鼎之腹宜有實者也其實在二陽之上</span>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4317:4340'>　　已過于溢而乃以陽剛之才求應于初爻初爻趾</span>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4340:4363'>　　已顛而四爻互兊為毁折故曰鼎折足覆公餗盖</span>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4363:4386'>　　四爻近君位為公之象也公為上所委任信如何</span>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4386:4409'>　　也而可以覆餗敗事也宜乎刑之至于渥則其凶</span>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4409:4436'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-12a' );" name="014-12a" class="pb">[014-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4436:4448'>　　可知矣折足可乎哉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4448:4459'>六五鼎黄耳金鉉利貞</span>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4459:4472'>　象曰鼎黄耳中以為實也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4472:4495'>　　六五爻為鼎黄耳黄取中色所以虛中受實為鼎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4495:4518'>　　之主然在鼎之上受鉉以舉鼎者乃耳也在鼎之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4518:4541'>　　外貫耳以舉鼎者乃鉉也上九爻以剛陽為金鉉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4541:4564'>　　而言于六五爻者謂六五爻以中䖏居無為之地</span>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4564:4587'>　　而来上九爻剛實之助也以貞為利君臣相正之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4587:4614'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-12b' );" name="014-12b" class="pb">[014-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4614:4621'>　　義得矣</span>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4621:4633'>上九鼎玉鉉大吉无不利</span>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4633:4646'>　象曰玉鉉在上剛柔節也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4646:4669'>　　上九爻居鼎之極而在趾腹耳之外乃鉉也鉉在</span>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4669:4692'>　　鼎之外勇于從五以成運動之功六五以柔中而</span>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4692:4715'>　　資上九之陽剛故曰金鉉金鉉者取其剛而已未</span>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4715:4738'>　　足以語其徳之全也至上爻處一卦之外以剛履</span>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4738:4761'>　　柔如玉之剛柔有節故曰玉鉉鉉之為用一而已</span>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4761:4788'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-13a' );" name="014-13a" class="pb">[014-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4788:4811'>　　在上爻為鉉在五爻為金鉉至是而後見其佐五</span>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4811:4834'>　　爻以成運動之功然功成矣而不居其功所以大</span>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4834:4847'>　　吉而亦無所不利者也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4847:4850'>震</span>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4850:4864'>　　　　震　上　　震　下</span>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4864:4922'>　　　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0306' title='KR0306' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0306.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0306' title='KR0306' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0306.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0320' title='KR0320' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0320.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0306' title='KR0306' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0306.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0306' title='KR0306' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0306.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0320' title='KR0320' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0320.png'/></span>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4922:4961'>　　　<span class='krp-note'>索/索</span>　<span class='krp-note'>徃來遂/厲  泥</span>　<span class='krp-note'>蘇/蘇</span>　<span class='krp-note'>來/厲</span>　<span class='krp-note'>虩/虩</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4961:4984'>　　震者動也一陽動乎二隂之下為雷之象合卦之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4984:5011'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-13b' );" name="014-13b" class="pb">[014-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='5011:5034'>　　二體則為洊雷震初九爻前震也前震人所駭懼</span>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='5034:5057'>　　故虩虩九四爻後震也後震人所暇豫故啞啞此</span>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='5057:5080'>　　前懼後喜之義也六二爻言震来謂前震之来也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='5080:5103'>　　六五爻言震徃謂前震徃矣後震復来也二近乎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='5103:5126'>　　初之震五近乎四之震最近則最危故皆以利言</span>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='5126:5149'>　　之然二之震言来厲震来虩虩也故喪貝五之震</span>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='5149:5172'>　　徃来厲笑言啞啞也故无喪此先喪後得之義也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='5172:5195'>　　六三爻去震為逺故言震蘓蘓而无眚上六爻去</span>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='5195:5222'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-14a' );" name="014-14a" class="pb">[014-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='5222:5245'>　　震亦逺故言震索索而无咎此又玩則招禍恐則</span>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='5245:5269'>　　致福之義也卦中六爻之義取象洊雷則是恐懼于</span>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='5269:5286'>　　先而修省于後其用震之道者歟</span>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='5286:5306'>震亨震来虩虩笑言啞啞震驚百里不喪匕鬯</span>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='5306:5328'>彖曰震亨震来虩虩恐致福也笑言啞啞後有則也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='5328:5351'>震驚百里驚逺而懼邇也出可以守宗廟社稷以為祭</span>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='5351:5355'>主也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='5355:5376'>　　王昭素按徐氏云出字上脱不喪匕鬯四字</span>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='5376:5403'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-14b' );" name="014-14b" class="pb">[014-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5403:5426'>　　震卦之所以言亨者初爻與四爻也二爻三爻五</span>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5426:5449'>　　爻上爻所震也虩虩者顧慮不安之貌啞啞者笑</span>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5449:5473'>　　聲不𤼵之貌震之方来而顧慮不安者乃所以為</span>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5473:5496'>　　致福之理此以前震論初爻也震之徃来而笑聲</span>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5496:5519'>　　莫知所自可以為後之則此以後震論四爻也然</span>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5519:5542'>　　四爻之遂泥不如初爻之吉者坤一索于初而後</span>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5542:5566'>　　震謂之長男其象為雷雷乃𤼵聲之時初爻有震</span>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5566:5589'>　　驚百里之威所以言吉四爻之遂泥者亦初爻之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5589:5616'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-15a' );" name="014-15a" class="pb">[014-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5616:5639'>　　餘威而已驚逺者謂五爻也懼邇者謂二爻也匕</span>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5639:5662'>　　鬯謂秬鬯鬱鬯灌地以求神之出皆長子主噐之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5662:5685'>　　象二爻居中正之位惟以恐懼致福所以喪貝五</span>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5685:5708'>　　爻得中而䖏尊位惟其後之有則所以无喪此不</span>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5708:5732'>　　喪匕鬯出則可以守宗廟社稷乃所以𤼵明震亨</span>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5732:5739'>　　之義也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5739:5753'>象曰洊雷震君子以恐懼修省</span>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5753:5776'>　　洊者如水洊至習坎之義重也重云者上下皆震</span>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5776:5803'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-15b' );" name="014-15b" class="pb">[014-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5803:5826'>　　故曰洊雷震初爻為前震恐致福也所以貴乎恐</span>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5826:5849'>　　懼耳四爻為後震後有則也所以貴乎修省耳然</span>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5849:5872'>　　必有取乎洊震者欲君子之恐懼修省不敢一日</span>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5872:5882'>　　間斷以自已也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5882:5896'>初九震来虩虩後笑言啞啞吉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5896:5917'>　象曰震来虩虩恐致福也笑言啞啞後有則也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5917:5940'>　　震者長男之卦也以初爻為主故初爻與卦皆言</span>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5940:5963'>　　震来虩虩笑言啞啞其詞雖同而其時不同盖卦</span>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5963:5990'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-16a' );" name="014-16a" class="pb">[014-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5990:6013'>　　以全體言故喜懼同時爻以各體言故前懼後喜</span>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='6013:6036'>　　以初爻本無啞啞之象于笑言字上獨加後之一</span>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='6036:6059'>　　字則知後字乃上卦之九四爻特舉九四之啞啞</span>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='6059:6082'>　　為初爻之虩虩發義自二爻至上爻皆不言吉而</span>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='6082:6105'>　　初爻之獨以吉稱國本所闗以恐懼致福而後遂</span>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='6105:6122'>　　有則故于初爻𤼵明吉之義也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='6122:6141'>六二震来厲億喪貝躋于九陵勿逐七日得</span>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='6141:6152'>　象曰震来厲乗剛也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='6152:6179'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-16b' );" name="014-16b" class="pb">[014-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='6179:6202'>　　二爻次于初爻乗初爻之剛故言震来厲震方来</span>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='6202:6225'>　　厲未免喪其所有耳古者寶龜而貨貝貝之為貨</span>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='6225:6248'>　　人所資者也今喪貝及十萬之數且極其髙逺躋</span>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='6248:6271'>　　于九陵所喪何其多耶惟二之長男柔順中正能</span>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='6271:6294'>　　以恐懼自守雖有所喪初不必逐七日可得矣七</span>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='6294:6317'>　　日者卦中之六爻周而復始故言七日可得以其</span>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='6317:6328'>　　當于所位故焉耳</span>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='6328:6339'>六三震蘓蘓震行无眚</span>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='6339:6366'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-17a' );" name="014-17a" class="pb">[014-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='6366:6378'>　象曰震蘓蘓位不當也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='6378:6401'>　　三爻逺于初爻者也不若二爻之最近而最恐然</span>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='6401:6424'>　　二爻以長男居正得中以厲存心喪貝必得三爻</span>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='6424:6447'>　　不當位故曰蘓蘓言神氣緩散而不伸也當前震</span>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='6447:6469'>　　之来行以避之僅以旡眚乃怠慢之所自取也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='6469:6476'>九四震遂泥</span>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='6476:6487'>　象曰震遂泥未光也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='6487:6510'>　　九四爻後震也陽剛失位與前震為不同初爻之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='6510:6537'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-17b' );" name="014-17b" class="pb">[014-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='6537:6560'>　　一陽方来震所以亨今一陽間于上下四隂爻之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='6560:6583'>　　間且互坎卦為未光其震遂泥而不釋故曰震遂</span>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='6583:6606'>　　泥泥讀為致逺恐泥之泥以其威極必䙝不若初</span>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='6606:6616'>　　之恐懼致吉也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='6616:6629'>六五震徃来厲億无喪有事</span>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='6629:6649'>　象曰震徃来厲危行也其事在中大无喪也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='6649:6672'>　　以六居五爻正長子主噐之時也五爻與二爻皆</span>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='6672:6695'>　　震之最近者其得喪亦在乎所䖏之位而巳二爻</span>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='6695:6722'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-18a' );" name="014-18a" class="pb">[014-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='6722:6745'>　　以震厲有喪有得五爻徃来皆厲何以有得无喪</span>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='6745:6769'>　　且成天下大有之事盖居得尊位正所以𤼵明不</span>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='6769:6792'>　　喪匕鬯出則可以守宗廟社稷以為祭主之義爻</span>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='6792:6815'>　　言億无喪象言大无喪皆衆多之事此出而主噐</span>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='6815:6829'>　　所以尤貴乎恐懼修省也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='6829:6852'>上六震索索視矍矍征凶震不于其躬于其鄰无咎婚</span>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='6852:6857'>媾有言</span>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='6857:6877'>　象曰震索索中未得也雖凶无咎畏鄰戒也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='6877:6904'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-18b' );" name="014-18b" class="pb">[014-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='6904:6927'>　　上六爻隂柔居震體之極雖比于六五爻之中而</span>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='6927:6950'>　　志不相得故曰中未得也索索者氣衰而不振之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='6950:6973'>　　貌矍矍者目動而不安之貌將安之乎所以征凶</span>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='6973:6996'>　　也然尚逺于四爻非若五爻之鄰于四爻也九四</span>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='6996:7019'>　　爻之威僅足以及我之鄰而不能及我之躬故曰</span>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='7019:7042'>　　震不于其躬于其鄰畏鄰戒而恐懼以臨之是以</span>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='7042:7065'>　　雖凶而无咎然而九四之爻乃陽之爻也上六之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='7065:7088'>　　爻乃隂之爻也隂與陽兩相配合婚媾之義不能</span>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='7088:7115'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-19a' );" name="014-19a" class="pb">[014-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='7115:7138'>　　恐懼于震来之始迨乎迫之始知所畏宜其婚媾</span>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='7138:7153'>　　有言此亦必不能免之者矣</span>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='7153:7156'>艮</span>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='7156:7170'>　　　　艮　上　　艮　下</span>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='7170:7228'>　　　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0320' title='KR0320' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0320.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0306' title='KR0306' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0306.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0306' title='KR0306' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0306.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0320' title='KR0320' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0320.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0306' title='KR0306' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0306.png'/>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0306' title='KR0306' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0306.png'/></span>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='7228:7248'>　　　<span class='krp-note'>敦/艮</span>　輔　身　限　腓　趾</span>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='7248:7271'>　　艮卦以兼山為止不徒止也止有行之理惟其時</span>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='7271:7294'>　　而已知時之説則知行與止之說聖人觀象設卦</span>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='7294:7321'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-19b' );" name="014-19b" class="pb">[014-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='7321:7344'>　　而艮以背為主寧非專于止者哉盖人之身惟背</span>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='7344:7367'>　　為止專于止則止其所未足以明艮止之義故諸</span>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='7367:7390'>　　爻皆以動體為象初六爻言艮其止六二爻言艮</span>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='7390:7413'>　　其腓九三爻言艮其限六四爻言艮其身六五爻</span>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='7413:7436'>　　言艮其輔至上九爻則言以厚終由爻義推之固</span>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='7436:7459'>　　以動體為言動而不適乎時則各囿于一偏非艮</span>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='7459:7482'>　　體之全亦為止其所止惟聖人得乎時止時行之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='7482:7505'>　　道是以卦中六爻之動隨所感而應之也故曰動</span>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='7505:7532'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-20a' );" name="014-20a" class="pb">[014-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='7532:7555'>　　靜不失其時其道光明行于其所當行止于其所</span>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='7555:7572'>　　可止行止皆當乃盡艮之道者也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='7572:7591'>艮其背不𫉬其身行其庭不見其人无咎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='7591:7614'>彖曰艮止也時止則止時行則行動靜不失其時其道</span>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='7614:7638'>光明艮其止止其所也上下敵應不相與也是以不𫉬</span>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='7638:7652'>其身行其庭不見其人无咎也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='7652:7671'>　　晁古易按艮其止只依卦辭作艮其背</span>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='7671:7694'>　　艮卦以止為義卦之定體也卦辭不過曰无咎而</span>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='7694:7721'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-20b' );" name="014-20b" class="pb">[014-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='7721:7745'>　　已未足以言聖人之止彖辭始𤼵明艮之之一字</span>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='7745:7768'>　　謂卦以艮名者時止也盖天下之理凡可止而不</span>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='7768:7791'>　　止與夫不當止而止者皆非聖人之時以舜之安</span>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='7791:7814'>　　汝止言之宜若淡然而無所事者及惟動丕應傒</span>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='7814:7837'>　　志則出而酬酢萬物之變是為時止則止時行則</span>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='7837:7860'>　　行動靜不失其時其道光明此行止以時乃聖人</span>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='7860:7883'>　　之事若言艮其止止其所也上下六位之爻皆敵</span>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='7883:7906'>　　應而不相與故曰艮其背背者以相背為義如兩</span>
<span class='tline' id='l367' data-llen='7906:7933'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-21a' );" name="014-21a" class="pb">[014-21a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l368' data-llen='7933:7957'>　　人背行則在我不𫉬其身至于在人則行其庭不</span>
<span class='tline' id='l369' data-llen='7957:7980'>　　見其人此止其所止之義非聖人時止時行之道</span>
<span class='tline' id='l370' data-llen='7980:8003'>　　者也是以不能隨所感而應之惟能有以補其不</span>
<span class='tline' id='l371' data-llen='8003:8021'>　　相與之過使之情通此无咎之謂也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l372' data-llen='8021:8036'>象曰兼山艮君子以思不出其位</span>
<span class='tline' id='l373' data-llen='8036:8059'>　　重艮為體兼山之象山以靜為義是以君子思不</span>
<span class='tline' id='l374' data-llen='8059:8082'>　　出其位夫所謂位者凡我所當為而不可過于有</span>
<span class='tline' id='l375' data-llen='8082:8105'>　　所為者皆位也天下之理初非甚髙難行不過君</span>
<span class='tline' id='l376' data-llen='8105:8132'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-21b' );" name="014-21b" class="pb">[014-21b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l377' data-llen='8132:8155'>　　止于仁臣止于敬父子止于慈與孝其諸君子思</span>
<span class='tline' id='l378' data-llen='8155:8178'>　　不出其位者乎然必以思言之思乃出于心憧憧</span>
<span class='tline' id='l379' data-llen='8178:8201'>　　徃来何有紀極惟能思不出其位則盡我所當為</span>
<span class='tline' id='l380' data-llen='8201:8214'>　　之理是得其所止者也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l381' data-llen='8214:8226'>初六艮其趾无咎利永貞</span>
<span class='tline' id='l382' data-llen='8226:8238'>　象曰艮其趾未失正也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l383' data-llen='8238:8261'>　　初六爻居卦之下乃足趾之象凡人之行也必先</span>
<span class='tline' id='l384' data-llen='8261:8284'>　　舉趾趾貴乎動而艮止之下動必失正正之于初</span>
<span class='tline' id='l385' data-llen='8284:8311'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-22a' );" name="014-22a" class="pb">[014-22a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l386' data-llen='8311:8334'>　　則不果于有行于正為未失何咎之有也然初六</span>
<span class='tline' id='l387' data-llen='8334:8357'>　　爻柔順未必能固守其正故利在永于貞盖貞則</span>
<span class='tline' id='l388' data-llen='8357:8380'>　　正固而有常矣是謂得其所止之理此所以致戒</span>
<span class='tline' id='l389' data-llen='8380:8391'>　　于艮之初六爻也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l390' data-llen='8391:8406'>六二艮其腓不拯其隨其心不快</span>
<span class='tline' id='l391' data-llen='8406:8419'>　象曰不拯其隨未退聽也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l392' data-llen='8419:8442'>　　六二爻居艮止之上其象為腓矣腓者足之腹也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l393' data-llen='8442:8465'>　　上與股相依股動則腓隨非能自動者也隨乎三</span>
<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='8465:8492'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-22b' );" name="014-22b" class="pb">[014-22b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='8492:8515'>　　而已何以知其所隨在三爻盖咸卦之九三爻言</span>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='8515:8538'>　　執其隨謂股也股居下卦之上剛而不中六二爻</span>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='8538:8561'>　　能以中正拯之則剛而不病于剛今六二爻以隂</span>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='8561:8584'>　　柔不能拯三而惟志于隨九三爻亦過剛不中不</span>
<span class='tline' id='l399' data-llen='8584:8607'>　　能退聽于二是以其心不快凡在下位而上無應</span>
<span class='tline' id='l400' data-llen='8607:8623'>　　援乃柔而不立艮其腓之謂也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l401' data-llen='8623:8636'>九三艮其限列其夤厲薰心</span>
<span class='tline' id='l402' data-llen='8636:8648'>　象曰艮其限危薰心也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l403' data-llen='8648:8675'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-23a' );" name="014-23a" class="pb">[014-23a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l404' data-llen='8675:8698'>　　九三上九爻皆成艮之主也上九居一卦之極而</span>
<span class='tline' id='l405' data-llen='8698:8721'>　　無所累于止以敦艮而止三爻下卦之上上下之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l406' data-llen='8721:8744'>　　際皆接于我而乃能固止其所是謂艮其限列其</span>
<span class='tline' id='l407' data-llen='8744:8767'>　　夤限與夤在人身皆為上下之交列而絶之能無</span>
<span class='tline' id='l408' data-llen='8767:8790'>　　厲乎厲既薰心而象辭復謂之危盖人心之天未</span>
<span class='tline' id='l409' data-llen='8790:8813'>　　始或忘心既不安其危特甚此三之言危薰心尤</span>
<span class='tline' id='l410' data-llen='8813:8826'>　　有甚于二之心不快也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l411' data-llen='8826:8835'>六四艮其身无咎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l412' data-llen='8835:8862'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-23b' );" name="014-23b" class="pb">[014-23b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l413' data-llen='8862:8874'>　象曰艮其身止諸躬也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l414' data-llen='8874:8897'>　　六四爻巳出下之體而進于上之體在人則為身</span>
<span class='tline' id='l415' data-llen='8897:8920'>　　之象爻言艮其身而象釋之以止諸躬何也躬即</span>
<span class='tline' id='l416' data-llen='8920:8943'>　　身之傴者也亦艮其背之義不言背而言躬躬猶</span>
<span class='tline' id='l417' data-llen='8943:8967'>　　足以見其身與不𫉬其身者為不同然自其身之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l418' data-llen='8967:8990'>　　傴者言之則見其背而不見其面故象于諸爻之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l419' data-llen='8990:9013'>　　下不言止而于此爻獨言止者亦止諸躬而已豈</span>
<span class='tline' id='l420' data-llen='9013:9026'>　　僅免于咎故曰无咎也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l421' data-llen='9026:9053'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-24a' );" name="014-24a" class="pb">[014-24a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l422' data-llen='9053:9065'>六五艮其輔言有序悔亡</span>
<span class='tline' id='l423' data-llen='9065:9077'>　象曰艮其輔以中正也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l424' data-llen='9077:9100'>　　六五爻居尊位而在衆體之上其位為輔輔頰車</span>
<span class='tline' id='l425' data-llen='9100:9123'>　　也言之所自出也夫君子出其言善則千里之外</span>
<span class='tline' id='l426' data-llen='9123:9146'>　　應之出其言不善則千里之外違之從違之間榮</span>
<span class='tline' id='l427' data-llen='9146:9169'>　　辱係焉能无悔乎五爻惟位乎中正觀其輔之所</span>
<span class='tline' id='l428' data-llen='9169:9192'>　　止而知其出乎言乃有序是以命令皆得其正當</span>
<span class='tline' id='l429' data-llen='9192:9204'>　　此悔所以能亡者也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l430' data-llen='9204:9231'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-24b' );" name="014-24b" class="pb">[014-24b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l431' data-llen='9231:9238'>上九敦艮吉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l432' data-llen='9238:9251'>　象曰敦艮之吉以厚終也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l433' data-llen='9251:9274'>　　上九爻居一卦之極全兼山之體夫山者厚也故</span>
<span class='tline' id='l434' data-llen='9274:9297'>　　曰敦艮盖敦至上九之爻乃成卦之主艮之終者</span>
<span class='tline' id='l435' data-llen='9297:9320'>　　也天下惟善終者為難耳晚節不移惟厚徳者始</span>
<span class='tline' id='l436' data-llen='9320:9343'>　　能之此君子之行其所止非厚徳不能以有立也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l437' data-llen='9343:9366'>　　夫人之止難于久終故節或移于晚守或失於終</span>
<span class='tline' id='l438' data-llen='9366:9389'>　　事或廢于久人之所同患也上九能敦厚于終止</span>
<span class='tline' id='l439' data-llen='9389:9416'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0048', 'WYG', '014-25a' );" name="014-25a" class="pb">[014-25a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l440' data-llen='9416:9439'>　　道之至善所以吉也艮卦之六爻惟此為吉者以</span>
<span class='tline' id='l441' data-llen='9439:9450'>　　其善于守終者也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l442' data-llen='9450:9453'>　</span>
